<doc id="1101947" wikidata="Q6943929" url="?curid=1101947" title="Mutineer (album)">
<text>Mutineer is the ninth studio album by American singer-songwriter Warren Zevon. The album was released on May 23, 1995, by Giant. The album largely consisted of home recordings. Bob Dylan covered &quot;Mutineer&quot; a number of times in concert after Zevon&#x27;s passing. A cover version plays over the credits of &quot;Otherwise&quot;, the finale of &quot;Futurama&quot; season nine.

==Track listing==
All tracks composed by Warren Zevon, except where indicated.

