<doc id="1102076" wikidata="Q1327489" url="?curid=1102076" title="Shōka (era)">
<text>was a after &quot;Kōgen&quot; and before &quot;Shōgen.&quot; This period spanned the years from March 1257 to March 1259. The reigning emperor was .

==Change of era==
* 1257 : The new era name was created to mark an event or a number of events. The previous era ended and a new one commenced in &quot;Kōgen&quot; 2.

==Events of the &quot;Shōka&quot; era==
* 1257 (&quot;Shōka 1&quot;): A major epidemic.

